overview:
FreeCashback.co.uk has been one of the leading incentive shopping websites in the UK since 2003. Thousands of members earn cashback every time they do their usual online shopping.

Through our association with hundreds of the leading internet stores, including many of high street shops and most traders in the UK such as banks and insurance companies, we can offer shoppers the best rewards and extra cash back.

The cashback our members earn is on top of the special incentives, offers, sale prices and online discounts provided by our retailers. Many of the shops allow you to use our exclusive discount vouchers in addition to the rewards.
